  "detailed_description": "In Ghost Run 3D you control a little ghost seen from behind where <br>you have to avoid obstacles in order to finish each level.<br><br>The Ghost have to escape from 3 dark worlds ( the cemetery, the <br>haunted forest and the cave), in order to reach the skies (the final <br>world) and finally be free. For this, jumping or going to sides are <br>the best ways to win through the 40 levels and their 4 worlds.<br><br><strong><u>The skies world... Will you be strong enough to reach it ?</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416290/extras/4abaead7a4541b788a7645de330e3a2f.poster.avif?t=1646042933\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416290/extras/4abaead7a4541b788a7645de330e3a2f.webm?t=1646042933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416290/extras/4abaead7a4541b788a7645de330e3a2f.mp4?t=1646042933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Playable with a xbox gamepad or a keyboard with the space bar key to jump <br>and arrows keys to go to the left or right. You can quit the game with the <br>\"escape\" key and start to play with the return/enter key.<br><br>The game saves automatically at each level.",
  "about_the_game": "In Ghost Run 3D you control a little ghost seen from behind where <br>you have to avoid obstacles in order to finish each level.<br><br>The Ghost have to escape from 3 dark worlds ( the cemetery, the <br>haunted forest and the cave), in order to reach the skies (the final <br>world) and finally be free. For this, jumping or going to sides are <br>the best ways to win through the 40 levels and their 4 worlds.<br><br><strong><u>The skies world... Will you be strong enough to reach it ?</u></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416290/extras/4abaead7a4541b788a7645de330e3a2f.poster.avif?t=1646042933\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416290/extras/4abaead7a4541b788a7645de330e3a2f.webm?t=1646042933\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1416290/extras/4abaead7a4541b788a7645de330e3a2f.mp4?t=1646042933\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Playable with a xbox gamepad or a keyboard with the space bar key to jump <br>and arrows keys to go to the left or right. You can quit the game with the <br>\"escape\" key and start to play with the return/enter key.<br><br>The game saves automatically at each level.",
